title: She's Dancing Like a Trender 6/9: Eminem x Kid Cudi, Michael Cohen, Seoul, Naya Rivera
itunes:title: She's Dancing Like a Trender 6/9: Eminem x Kid Cudi, Michael Cohen, Seoul, Naya Rivera
description:
On this edition of She's Dancing Like a Trender Miles and DJ Danl discuss Eminem and Kid Cudi releasing a collab, Michael Cohen is going back to jail after violating the details of his COVID related home sentencing, the Mayor of Seoul has passed away amid sexual assault allegations, and Naya Rivera is still missing in Lake Piru.
